PyFacebook
===============================================
http://github.com/sciyoshi/pyfacebook/

sudo ln -s `pwd`/packages/pyfacebook/facebook /usr/lib/python2.6/dist-packages/facebook

sudo ln -s `pwd`/packages/pyfacebook/bin/djangofb.py /usr/local/bin/djangofb.py

