Pinax
===============================================
1. Download Pinax release version
2. apt-get install python-virtualenv
3. Get and install http://www.doughellmann.com/downloads/virtualenvwrapper-1.20.tar.gz

SMS Extraction from iPhone
===============================================
In ~/Library/MobileSync/backup/[some id]/
3d0d7e5fb2ce288813306e4d4636395e047a3d28.mddata or .mdbackup file contains
the SMS messages

http://supercrazyawesome.com/ (iphone backup extractor can be used to retrieve from the iphone the SMS data)
After extraction it will be under Library/SMS/sms.db

http://damon.durandfamily.org/archives/000487.html (contains db schema)

